<paragraph blockId="16.[136,1452,698,1589]" pageId="16" pageNumber="129">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,715,734,760]" pageId="16" pageNumber="129">Habitat, phenology and conservation status:</emphasis>
—Epiphyte. Broad-leaved evergreen lowland forests at elevations 
<quantity box="[136,263,770,797]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="16" pageNumber="129" unit="m" value="350.0" valueMax="400.0" valueMin="300.0">300–400 m</quantity>
a.s.l. Fl. April–June. Very rare. Suggested 
<collectionCode box="[742,810,770,796]" pageId="16" pageNumber="129">IUCN</collectionCode>
Red List status – EN.
</paragraph>
